room_title: Escape room "Prison Break" by Red Door Escape Room Concord in Concord
room_description: The exotic food, rich culture, and beautiful landscape of Asia enticed you to vacation there.  However, misfortune comes upon you suddenly as an infamous terrorist organization ambushes your tour group and takes you as prisoners to their compound.  Escape as quickly as possible before you find yourself at the mercy of their ruthlessness.
